---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="hairline-t bg-white">
  <div class="container-content py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center" aria-label="헤이보카 홈">
          <img
            src="/images/logo_h.png"
            alt="Hey, Voca!"
            width="106"
            height="25"
            class="h-[22px] w-auto select-none"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-body-sm leading-relaxed text-sub text-pretty">
          당신이 외운 단어, 우리가 기억합니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav aria-label="법적 고지" class="text-body-sm">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-caption font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-mute">법적 고지</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-ink hover:text-primary-600">개인정보처리방침</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms-of-service" class="text-ink hover:text-primary-600">서비스 이용약관</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="text-body-sm leading-relaxed text-sub">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-caption font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-mute">사업자 정보</h2>
        <dl class="space-y-1.5">
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-mute">상호</dt><dd class="text-ink">슬기로운 사업</dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-mute">대표</dt><dd class="text-ink">조건호</dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-mute">사업자등록번호</dt><dd class="text-ink">315-27-01645</dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-mute">이메일</dt><dd><a href="mailto:ceo@ghmate.com" class="text-ink hover:text-primary-600">ceo@ghmate.com</a></dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-mute">주소</dt><dd class="text-ink">부산광역시 부산진구 동천로 116, 3층 오픈오피스 12호</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="hairline-t mt-12 pt-6 text-caption text-mute">
      © {year} 슬기로운 사업. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
